The Ethics and Anti -Corruption detectives  in Mombasa are holding a Mombasa tycoon, who was arrested last night  for allegedly attempting to bribe Nairobi Governor Mike Sonko with one million shillings . Praful Kumar, is said to have gone to the governor’s residence at Kanamai with an intention of bribing him to approve the building of a hotel in Gigiri, Nairobi .  